                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d795">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 841.857/30</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Germany</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_GJW1"
                        type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Gerard</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Berlin</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-09-10">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 10, 1915, noon.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/> [<hi rend="italic">Received September 11, 10.15 a. m.</hi>]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>2866. Your 2155, September 6[7], 6 p. m.<note n="1" xml:id="d795fn1">
                        <hi rend="italic">Ante</hi>, <ref target="#pg_537">p. 537</ref>.</note>
                    Delivered request for report on <hi rend="italic">Hesperian</hi> to <persName
                        corresp="#p_JGEGV1">Von Jagow</persName> last night. He said that he did not
                    see what business it was of the United States unless American citizens had lost
                    their lives, and said unless American lives had been lost he would give you no
                    report. He intimated that the explosion was caused by a mine. Probably that will
                    be the German position.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_GJW1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Gerard</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
